        </div>

        <p className="text-center mt-8 text-gray-400 text-[10px] font-medium px-8 uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose">
          By continuing, you agree to Hotel Anandam's <br/>
          <span className="text-orange-500 font-bold cursor-pointer hover:underline">Terms of Service</span> and 
          <span className="text-orange-500 font-bold cursor-pointer hover:underline ml-1">Privacy Policy</span>.
